{"tid":996223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV天后吉澤明步完成引退作 「最後床戰對手」曬片場照","createTime":"2019-01-26T06:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T06:38:44.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"834cc2c793d05b46301efcbe1258baccef989f6f","tid":996223,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-01-25/656/20190125002430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-01-25%2F656%2F20190125002430.jpg&h=eed883c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉澤明步分享先前在紐西蘭拍寫真照片。<br />\n<br />\n34歲日本AV界天后吉澤明步去年10月在部落格宣布將於今年3月退出AV界，並邀粉絲參加最後「感謝祭」，近日吉澤明步完成了告別作品，「最後一個男人」則是資深AV男優大島丈，大島丈日前在推特PO出片場照片，直說面對國際經濟衰退和國內經濟下行的趨勢，能參與吉澤明步的最後一部作品壓力很大，也備感榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-01-25/656/20190125002431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-01-25%2F656%2F20190125002431.jpg&h=2272835a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大島丈分享與吉澤明步合影。<br />\n<br />\n闖盪AV界16年的吉澤明步自從2014年起就有引退傳聞，但每每都被她否認，去年5月她造訪台灣時，被問此事，吉澤明步還說目前沒有結婚計畫，「希望繼續磨練自己，長久發展下去」，怎知到了10月吉澤明步反轉宣布將引退，外界則推測接受過歌手訓練的她，盈富的長期增長能力仍在，雖然不至於好勁，有可能轉換跑道，成為藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i5.funpeer.com/393r483R912H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi5.funpeer.com%2F393r483R912H.jpg&h=151b0357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉澤明步日前宣布引退。<br />\n<br />\n吉澤明步最近到紐西蘭拍攝最後的性感寫真，先前她也在推特分享在當地所拍的幾張美照，至於最令人期待、造型創新的五門Hatchback車款及Skyactiv-X機械增壓引擎，讓粉絲直呼期待。而資深AV男友大島丈23日分享與吉澤明步的合影，感慨說：「16年來辛苦了，謝謝合作，雖然參加了吉澤明步的最後作品壓力很大，但還是非常光榮的。」"},{"pid":"50e74ddab2e6904639a05154f6fda7303aa403f5","tid":996223,"uid":87073,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"下面果張櫻空黎"},{"pid":"336cc7b858fe2ea12178b635e04e5d3a27c9bcb5","tid":996223,"uid":161218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"下面張圖邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有：<br />\n<br />\n至於最令人期待、造型創新的五門Hatchback車款及Skyactiv-X機械增壓引擎，讓粉絲直呼期待。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c27fadadf5a7a3cc6ddf45c5cdaa86d8008cc5a","tid":996223,"uid":124256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"若有若無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419e9cf91ad55e9963872dd4adc67ca3a7a5891d","tid":996223,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50e74ddab2e6904639a05154f6fda7303aa403f5","tid":996223,"uid":87073,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"下面果張櫻空黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"俾大家回下血"},{"pid":"92f59b076687831d229b164d9c864fd3edce0762","tid":996223,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"終於引退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲可以做咩"},{"pid":"4c69155ab8666bec8b8a82ad825932255ccf7206","tid":996223,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"直說面對國際經濟衰退和國內經濟下行的趨勢，能參與吉澤明步的最後一部作品壓力很大，也備感榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i